<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>AutoTest Station | 架构与治理全景</title>
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --teal: #0f766e;
      --teal-light: #14b8a6;
      --amber: #b45309;
      --amber-light: #d97706;
      --violet: #7c3aed;
      --bg: #f5ecdd;
      --surface: #fffaf2;
      --text: #2d241d;
      --text-secondary: #6f6358;
      --border: rgba(102, 69, 33, 0.14);
      --shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(51, 36, 22, 0.12);
      --shadow-sm: 0 4px 12px rgba(51, 36, 22, 0.08);
      --radius: 18px;
      --radius-sm: 12px;
      --heading-font: "Georgia", "Times New Roman", "Songti SC", serif;
    }

    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

    body {
      font-family: "Segoe UI Variable Text", "Avenir Next", "PingFang SC", "Microsoft YaHei", -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(15, 118, 110, 0.16), transparent 32%),
        radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(180, 83, 9, 0.12), transparent 28%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #f5ecdd 0%, #f0e6d8 46%, #eadfce 100%);
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.6;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      overflow-x: hidden;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }

    a { color: inherit; }

    /* ── Nav ── */
    .top-nav {
      position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
      height: 56px; padding: 0 36px;
      background: rgba(250, 250, 250, 0.82);
      backdrop-filter: blur(18px); -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      z-index: 100;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
    }
    .nav-brand, .nav-links { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 18px; }
    .top-nav a {
      text-decoration: none; color: var(--text-secondary);
      font-size: 0.84rem; font-weight: 600; transition: color 0.2s ease;
    }
    .top-nav a:hover { color: var(--text); }

    /* ── Section base ── */
    .hero, .section {
      max-width: 1040px; margin: 0 auto;
      padding-left: 36px; padding-right: 36px;
      opacity: 0; transform: translateY(28px);
      transition: opacity 0.8s ease, transform 0.8s ease;
    }
    .hero.visible, .section.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }

    .hero { padding-top: 128px; padding-bottom: 72px; }

    .hero-badge {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
      padding: 4px 14px 4px 8px; border-radius: 999px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--teal), var(--amber));
      color: #fff; font-size: 0.76rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 22px;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-family: var(--heading-font);
      font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 5vw, 3.6rem);
      font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.02em;
      line-height: 1.12; margin-bottom: 14px;
    }

    .hero-subtitle {
      font-size: clamp(1.06rem, 2.4vw, 1.42rem);
      color: var(--text-secondary); max-width: 860px;
      margin-bottom: 28px; letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    }

    .section-title, .bento-card h3, .mini-main h3 {
      font-family: var(--heading-font); letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    }

    .tech-stack { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px; }
    .tech-tag {
      padding: 6px 14px; border-radius: 999px;
      background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border);
      color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 600;
    }

    /* ── Stats row ── */
    .stats-row {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 14px;
      margin-top: 42px;
    }
    .stat-card {
      background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 20px; text-align: center;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
    }
    .stat-value {
      font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--teal), var(--amber));
      -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
    }
    .stat-label {
      font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--text-secondary);
      margin-top: 4px; font-weight: 600;
    }

    /* ── Section ── */
    .section { padding-top: 84px; padding-bottom: 30px; }
    .section-label {
      font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: var(--teal); margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .section-title {
      font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.4rem);
      font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.03em; margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .section-copy {
      color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 1rem;
      max-width: 820px; margin-bottom: 34px;
    }

    /* ── Bento grid ── */
    .bento-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 16px; }
    .bento-grid-3 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 16px; }
    .bento-card {
      background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 28px; box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      transition: transform 0.25s ease, box-shadow 0.25s ease;
    }
    .bento-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.07);
    }
    .bento-card.wide { grid-column: 1 / -1; }
    .bento-icon {
      width: 48px; height: 48px; border-radius: 12px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 1.35rem; margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .bento-icon.teal { background: rgba(15, 118, 110, 0.12); }
    .bento-icon.amber { background: rgba(180, 83, 9, 0.12); }
    .bento-icon.violet { background: rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.12); }
    .bento-icon.green { background: rgba(22, 163, 74, 0.12); }

    .bento-card h3 { font-size: 1.14rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .bento-card p { color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.7; }

    .bento-tags { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px; margin-top: 16px; }
    .tag { padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 999px; font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 700; }
    .tag.teal { background: #ccfbf1; color: var(--teal); }
    .tag.amber { background: #fef3c7; color: var(--amber); }
    .tag.violet { background: #f3e8ff; color: var(--violet); }
    .tag.green { background: #dcfce7; color: #16a34a; }

    /* ── Architecture diagram ── */
    .arch-diagram {
      background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 32px; margin-top: 18px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }
    .arch-layers { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0; }
    .arch-layer {
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 18px;
      padding: 18px 24px; border: 1px solid var(--border);
      cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.25s ease;
      background: #fff;
    }
    .arch-layer:first-child { border-radius: var(--radius) var(--radius) 0 0; }
    .arch-layer:last-child { border-radius: 0 0 var(--radius) var(--radius); }
    .arch-layer:not(:last-child) { border-bottom: none; }
    .arch-layer.active { background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(15, 118, 110, 0.06), rgba(180, 83, 9, 0.06)); border-color: rgba(15, 118, 110, 0.2); }
    .arch-layer:hover { background: #faf8f4; }
    .arch-layer-icon { font-size: 1.5rem; flex-shrink: 0; }
    .arch-layer-info { flex: 1; }
    .arch-layer-name { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; }
    .arch-layer-desc { font-size: 0.84rem; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-top: 2px; }
    .arch-layer-count {
      flex-shrink: 0; padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 999px;
      background: #f1f5f9; font-size: 0.78rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-secondary);
    }
    .arch-detail {
      margin-top: 18px; padding: 22px; background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius);
    }
    .arch-detail h4 { font-size: 1rem; margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: 700; }
    .arch-detail-list {
      padding-left: 18px; color: var(--text-secondary);
      font-size: 0.88rem; line-height: 1.75;
    }
    .arch-detail-tags { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px; margin-top: 14px; }

    /* ── Truth flow ── */
    .truth-flow {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr auto 1fr auto 1fr; gap: 0; align-items: start;
      margin-top: 18px;
    }
    .truth-node {
      background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 22px; box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
    }
    .truth-node h4 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 6px; }
    .truth-node p { font-size: 0.86rem; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.6; }
    .truth-node ul { padding-left: 16px; font-size: 0.84rem; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.7; margin-top: 8px; }
    .truth-arrow {
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 1.4rem; color: var(--teal); padding-top: 30px;
    }

    /* ── Table ── */
    .truth-table {
      width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-top: 18px;
      background: var(--surface); border-radius: var(--radius); overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm); border: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .truth-table th, .truth-table td {
      padding: 12px 16px; text-align: left; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      font-size: 0.86rem;
    }
    .truth-table th {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(15, 118, 110, 0.08), rgba(180, 83, 9, 0.08));
      font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.78rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    }
    .truth-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
    .truth-table td:first-child { font-weight: 600; }

    /* ── Workspace tree ── */
    .ws-tree {
      background: #111827; color: #e2e8f0; border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 24px 28px; font-family: Consolas, "SFMono-Regular", monospace;
      font-size: 0.82rem; line-height: 1.8; margin-top: 18px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow); overflow-x: auto;
    }
    .ws-tree .dir { color: #93c5fd; }
    .ws-tree .file { color: #a5b4fc; }
    .ws-tree .comment { color: #6b7280; }
    .ws-tree .required { color: #34d399; }
    .ws-tree .optional { color: #fbbf24; }

    /* ── Station mockup ── */
    .station-mockup {
      background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius); overflow: hidden; box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      margin-top: 18px;
    }
    .mockup-toolbar {
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 14px 18px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(15, 118, 110, 0.92), rgba(180, 83, 9, 0.85));
      color: #fff;
    }
    .mockup-dots { display: flex; gap: 6px; }
    .mockup-dots span { width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); }
    .mockup-title { font-size: 0.92rem; font-weight: 700; }
    .mockup-body { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 200px 1fr 260px; gap: 0; min-height: 340px; }
    .mockup-sidebar {
      padding: 14px; border-right: 1px solid var(--border); background: #faf9f6;
    }
    .mockup-item {
      padding: 8px 10px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 0.78rem;
      margin-bottom: 6px; color: var(--text-secondary);
      border: 1px solid transparent; cursor: default;
    }
    .mockup-item.active {
      background: rgba(15, 118, 110, 0.08); border-color: rgba(15, 118, 110, 0.18);
      color: var(--text); font-weight: 700;
    }
    .mockup-center { padding: 16px; }
    .mockup-tabs {
      display: flex; gap: 0; border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border); margin-bottom: 14px;
    }
    .mockup-tab {
      padding: 8px 14px; font-size: 0.78rem; font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--text-secondary); border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
      margin-bottom: -2px; cursor: default;
    }
    .mockup-tab.active { color: var(--teal); border-bottom-color: var(--teal); }
    .mockup-center-content { font-size: 0.84rem; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.7; }
    .mockup-metric-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 14px; }
    .mockup-metric {
      text-align: center; padding: 12px; background: #f8f7f4;
      border-radius: 10px; border: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .mockup-metric-val { font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--text); }
    .mockup-metric-label { font-size: 0.7rem; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-top: 2px; }
    .mockup-report {
      padding: 14px; border-left: 1px solid var(--border); background: #faf9f6;
      font-size: 0.78rem;
    }
    .mockup-report h4 { font-size: 0.84rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .report-row {
      display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
      padding: 6px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
    }
    .report-row .name { color: var(--text); font-weight: 600; }
    .report-row .rate { font-weight: 700; }
    .report-row .rate.good { color: #16a34a; }
    .report-row .rate.warn { color: var(--amber); }
    .report-row .rate.bad { color: #dc2626; }
    .report-copy-btn {
      margin-top: 12px; width: 100%; padding: 8px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--teal), var(--amber));
      color: #fff; border: none; border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 0.78rem; font-weight: 700; cursor: default;
    }

    /* ── Timeline ── */
    .process-timeline {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr); gap: 14px;
      margin-top: 18px; position: relative;
    }
    .process-timeline::before {
      content: ""; position: absolute;
      top: 28px; left: 10%; right: 10%;
      height: 2px; background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--teal), var(--amber));
      z-index: 0;
    }
    .process-step {
      position: relative; z-index: 1; text-align: center;
      background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 22px 14px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm); transition: transform 0.25s ease;
    }
    .process-step:hover { transform: translateY(-3px); }
    .process-step-icon {
      width: 40px; height: 40px; border-radius: 50%; margin: 0 auto 10px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 1.2rem; background: #fff; border: 2px solid var(--teal);
    }
    .process-step h4 { font-size: 0.88rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 6px; }
    .process-step p { font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.5; }

    /* ── Roadmap ── */
    .roadmap-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 16px; margin-top: 18px; }
    .roadmap-card {
      background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 24px; box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
      position: relative; overflow: hidden;
    }
    .roadmap-card::before {
      content: ""; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 4px;
    }
    .roadmap-card.p0::before { background: linear-gradient(to right, #dc2626, #f87171); }
    .roadmap-card.p1::before { background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--amber), var(--amber-light)); }
    .roadmap-card.p2::before { background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--teal), var(--teal-light)); }
    .roadmap-priority {
      font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 800; text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em; margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .roadmap-card.p0 .roadmap-priority { color: #dc2626; }
    .roadmap-card.p1 .roadmap-priority { color: var(--amber); }
    .roadmap-card.p2 .roadmap-priority { color: var(--teal); }
    .roadmap-card h4 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .roadmap-card ul {
      padding-left: 16px; font-size: 0.84rem; color: var(--text-secondary);
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    /* ── Footer ── */
    .footer {
      max-width: 1040px; margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 56px 36px 80px;
      color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    /* ── Responsive ── */
    @media (max-width: 860px) {
      .bento-grid, .bento-grid-3, .truth-flow, .roadmap-grid,
      .process-timeline, .mockup-body, .stats-row {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
      .truth-arrow { transform: rotate(90deg); padding: 10px 0; }
      .top-nav { padding: 0 20px; }
      .hero, .section, .footer { padding-left: 20px; padding-right: 20px; }
      .nav-links { display: none; }
      .mockup-body { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .mockup-sidebar, .mockup-report { border: none; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <nav class="top-nav">
    <div class="nav-brand">
      <a href="../../index.html">reGeorge</a>
      <a href="#hero">AutoTest Station</a>
    </div>
    <div class="nav-links">
      <a href="#arch">三层架构</a>
      <a href="#truth">数据真相</a>
      <a href="#workspace">资产治理</a>
      <a href="#portal">工作站</a>
      <a href="#process">流程生命周期</a>
      <a href="#governance">治理路线</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- ════ Hero ════ -->
  <header class="hero" id="hero">
    <div class="hero-badge"><span>🧩</span><span>Architecture &amp; Governance</span></div>
    <h1>需求自动化工作站</h1>
    <div class="hero-subtitle">
      从脚本仓库演进到 <strong>服务编排层 + 工作站门户 + 需求资产库</strong>。<br>
      工作站负责入口，meta.json / board_state.json 负责真相，日报周报和 HTML 总结全部由真相派生。
    </div>
    <div class="tech-stack">
      <div class="tech-tag">skills → services → scripts</div>
      <div class="tech-tag">meta.json 单一真相</div>
      <div class="tech-tag">版本化 workspace</div>
      <div class="tech-tag">ATP scope 聚合</div>
      <div class="tech-tag">三栏工作站</div>
      <div class="tech-tag">报告派生制</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stats-row">
      <div class="stat-card">
        <div class="stat-value">19+</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Services 编排层</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card">
        <div class="stat-value">11</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Skill 能力组</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card">
        <div class="stat-value">22+</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Active Workstreams</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-card">
        <div class="stat-value">4</div>
        <div class="stat-label">版本并行管理</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- ════ Part 01: Architecture ════ -->
  <section class="section" id="arch">
    <div class="section-label">Part 01 · 三层架构</div>
    <div class="section-title">skills → services → scripts：能力封装、业务编排、薄入口</div>
    <div class="section-copy">底层 skill 封装单一 API 能力，service 层编排跨 skill 业务流程并统一返回 ServiceResult，script 只做参数解析和调用。工作站（station）作为唯一人工门户，调用 service 层完成所有操作。</div>

    <div class="arch-diagram">
      <div class="arch-layers" id="archLayers"></div>
      <div class="arch-detail" id="archDetail">
        <h4 id="archDetailTitle">选择一层查看详情</h4>
        <ul class="arch-detail-list" id="archDetailList"></ul>
        <div class="arch-detail-tags" id="archDetailTags"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ════ Part 02: Data Truth ════ -->
  <section class="section" id="truth">
    <div class="section-label">Part 02 · 数据真相</div>
    <div class="section-title">meta.json + board_state.json：每类信息只有一个写入位置</div>
    <div class="section-copy">meta.json 承载需求长期状态（阶段、用例、备注、文档索引），board_state.json 承载运行态（ATP 绑定、快照、UI 状态）。HTML 报告、日报、周报全部是派生产物。</div>

    <div class="truth-flow">
      <div class="truth-node">
        <h4>📥 输入源</h4>
        <p>CSV 导入、手工录入、飞书同步</p>
        <ul>
          <li>测试用例 CSV 初始导入</li>
          <li>工作站界面手工维护</li>
          <li>飞书表格 API 同步</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="truth-arrow">→</div>
      <div class="truth-node">
        <h4>💎 唯一真相</h4>
        <p>meta.json + board_state.json</p>
        <ul>
          <li>需求状态、用例行、备注</li>
          <li>ATP 绑定与执行快照</li>
          <li>导航状态与 UI 偏好</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="truth-arrow">→</div>
      <div class="truth-node">
        <h4>📊 派生产物</h4>
        <p>所有展示与报告</p>
        <ul>
          <li>工作站各 tab 视图</li>
          <li>右侧总结报告表格</li>
          <li>日报/周报草稿</li>
          <li>交互总结 HTML</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <table class="truth-table">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>信息类型</th>
          <th>唯一真相源</th>
          <th>展示位置</th>
          <th>可手工改?</th>
        </tr>
